openjava.ptree.util

Class ParseTreeVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • openjava.ptree.util.ParseTreeVisitor
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    EvaluationShuttle, SourceCodeWriter

    public abstract class ParseTreeVisitor
extends java.lang.Object
    The class ParseTreeVisitor is a Visitor role in the Visitor pattern and visits ParseTree objects as the role of Element.
